Of course they know.

585
00:25:26,109 --> 00:25:27,959
Why should they choose
thelady anne?

586
00:25:27,994 --> 00:25:30,462
Blessed if i know.

587
00:25:30,497 --> 00:25:33,215
Well, it isn't really
such a different story.

