714
00:30:11,394 --> 00:30:11,993
the writer.

715
00:30:12,028 --> 00:30:13,745
Surely you've heard
about him?

716
00:30:13,780 --> 00:30:16,114
We used to call him
otto of roses.

717
00:30:16,149 --> 00:30:17,999
Such a one with the ladies.

718
00:30:18,034 --> 00:30:20,502
You wouldn't think so

719
00:30:20,537 --> 00:30:21,870
