go get some fresh air?

761
00:31:55,131 --> 00:31:57,599
It'll do you good.

762
00:31:57,634 --> 00:31:58,850
Thank you
so much.

763
00:32:41,643 --> 00:32:45,396
Now what's going on?

764
00:32:45,431 --> 00:32:47,265
Hmm?

765
00:32:47,300 --> 00:32:48,516
